  "worklog": "## 2026-03-30 06:13 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 3] Strategy Scope Validated: No Adjacent Hours or Markets to Add\n\n**Task:** Evaluate strategy expansion: could we add more active hours or new markets (ETH, SOL)?\n\n**Finding:**\n\n1. **Adjacent hours are all losers:**\n\n| Hour | WR | Trades | Est $/day | Verdict |\n|------|-----|--------|-----------|---------|\n| 10h | 44.4% | 9 | -$1.4 | \u274c Pre-London noise |\n| 13h | 42.9% | 7 | -$1.4 | \u274c NY open chaos |\n| 18h | 55.6% | 18 | +$1.9 | \u274c Marginal, not worth risk |\n| 21h | 43.8% | 16 | -$2.8 | \u274c Post-NY decay |\n\n14h/15h showed 58-60% WR but ALL pre-V3 (weaker filters). With V3+ conviction requirements, likely 50-55% = unprofitable.\n\n2. **No ETH/SOL 5-min markets on PM.** API search returned 0 short-term ETH/SOL markets. Only BTC 5-min exists as a dynamic rolling market. Long-term crypto markets exist (e.g., \"Will BTC hit $1M?\") but our strategy is 5-min specific.\n\n3. **V4 bot stability confirmed** \u2014 running for 2+ minutes post-deploy, correctly logging OUTSIDE_ACTIVE_HOURS with bias and PM prices. F&G loaded at startup (8/Extreme Fear, +0.10 edge, 1.25x size).\n\n**My thinking:** Our edge is narrow and deep, not wide and shallow. BTC 5-min at 11h/12h/19h/20h with V4 filters is the right scope. Growth comes from:\n- Better WR per trade (V4 changes: copy disabled, VWAP relaxed, F&G)\n- More trades per active hour (VWAP relaxation unblocks ~20 signals/week)\n- Slightly larger positions (F&G 1.25x at current fear levels)\n- NOT from adding marginal hours or untested markets\n\n**Decision:** No changes to active hours or market scope. Strategy expansion will come from V4 parameter improvements, not surface area. Next growth vector: V5 idea \u2014 when $1,000 balance reached, increase max_position_pct from 1.2% to 1.5%.\n\n**Next P3 heartbeat:** After V4 produces 10+ trades, analyze whether the combined changes (VWAP relaxation + F&G boost + copy disabled) are net positive. Design V5 position sizing schedule.\n\n## 2026-03-30 06:08 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 2] V4 DEPLOYED LIVE \u2014 3 Changes Applied\n\n**Task:** Deploy V4 package to live PM bot. All 3 changes had been designed, patched, and tested in prior heartbeats. Deploy early (5h before active trading) to catch any crashes.\n\n**Changes deployed:**\n1. **Copy boost disabled** (`copy_conviction_boost = 0`) \u2014 bot farms were poisoning signal, WR 77% without vs 45% with\n2. **VWAP relaxation at 11h/12h** \u2014 hour-adaptive: relaxed at peak WR hours (88%/82%), mandatory at 19h/20h. Recovers est. $18/day in blocked signals.\n3. **Fear & Greed integration** \u2014 edge modifier (+0.10 at F&G=8) and position multiplier (1.25x at F&G=8). Refreshes hourly.\n\n**Deployment log:**\n```\n06:11:01 - \ud83d\udcca F&G: 8 (Extreme Fear) \u2192 edge mod +0.10, size 1.25x\n06:11:01 - \ud83d\udcb0 CLOB Balance: $922.45\n06:11:02 - \ud83d\udcca Bootstrapped 100 candles\n06:11:02 - \ud83d\udd01 Entering main trading loop...\n```\n\n**V4 impact estimate (combined):**\n- VWAP relaxation: +$18/day from unblocked 11h/12h trades\n- Copy disabled: WR improvement from ~55% \u2192 ~65%+ (removing 45% WR noise tra",
